Could be great in GM's

Explosive Payload should proc One for All

PvP: This thing is a godsend in PVP. With rolls like Rangefinder/Explosive, Killing Wind/Opening Shot, and Rapid Hit/Eye of the Storm, and Range Finder/Eye of the Storm (just to name a few perk combos), this 120 outshines all with it's fantastic perk pool. I've personally been using a hammer forged, accurized, killing wind, and opening shot roll for ages and it never fails to be as reliable as ever.
